title: Volleyball Roundup: Lady Bears lose at home
text:
Volleyball Roundup: Lady Bears lose at home 10:54 p.m. EDT October 19, 2015 CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
Carrollton 3, River View 2 
The Lady Bears (12-9) were defeated in five sets at home Monday against Carrollton in Division II tourney play 25-19, 24-26, 21-25, 25-17 and 13-15. 
River View was led by Grace Hayes with 14 kills and Sydnee Bice racked up 33 assists. Cassidy Whiteus had 28 digs and Grace Wherley added 11. Read or Share this story: http://ohne.ws/1LHt1cB TOP VIDEOS
